name: Luceo Voucher
description:
Can't decide or know a hard person to buy for?

Problem solved - We have $50 vouchers. Buy one or more, just fill in your quantity from the drop down box.

Write the gift recipient's address in the notes section at the Cart Checkout and we'll send it their way for you.  Or we can send it direct to you. 

When they find something their heart desires they can email us and we will get a special order ready for them minus their voucher value.  

Too easy. A much appreciated gift, I am sure!

NB. Valid for one year from purchase date.

The I.D. Bar Necklace with Star charm with a hammered finish available in 14k Gold Filled or Sterling Silver.  

I.D. Bar comes blank, customise it yourself with names, numbers or a secret.  Adjustable chain with a length of 18"/20".

name: Butterfly Lariat Necklace
description:
Made by French ceremist; Virginie Callea, this gorgeous necklace is feminine, beautiful.

White butterflies float along this vintage chain necklace made using the finest australian Southern Ice porcelain, they were hand shaped, colored and glazed.

name: Cleopatra Tunic
description:
Channel your inner queen with this gorgeous beaded & embroidered tunic in white, knee length with front pockets. Stunning and will be a classic favourite for years to come.

Designed by new Queensland label S O L I T O.

name: Bananas with the Baianas
description: Designed by Australian label, Binny.  Summer's favourite - a white cotton lace dress, mid length with below elbow tie sleeve.
